name: Mark Maxwell
description: I really suck at describing myself over the computer but i will try to. This thing does ask you the right questions because it leaves you wondering what you should write here. I am an easy going person and i am a wonderful person to be around. I am one of those people that will let you have her coat and make sure that you where having fun before i would do anything else. But ofcourse i would expect the man to do the same things for me. Ofcourse relationships are 50 50 and that is what i do believe in.
